                                     ADA
                         I'm Ada Monroe.

                                     INMAN
                         I'm Inman.

                                     ADA
                         Inman?

                                     INMAN
                         W. P. Inman.

                                     ADA
                         W. P. Inman.

                                     INMAN
                         Repeating a thing doesn't improve 
                         it.
                              (shrugs)
                         People call me Inman.

                                     ADA
                         If you were to take a glass of 
                         lemonade your friends might stop 
                         staring. Inman.

                                     INMAN
                         They're not my friends.

