                                     INMAN
                         Thank you.

                                     ADA
                         And what do you do?

                                     INMAN
                         I work wood. Got a piece of land. 
                         Mostly work wood.

                                     ADA
                         Clear fields?

                                     INMAN
                              (uncomfortable)
                         I can clear a field.

                                     ADA
                         So, was there something in particular 
                         you wished to say to me?

                                     INMAN
                              (thinks about it)
                         Not that comes to me.
                              (hands back the glass)
                         I'll say thank you for the lemonade.

